      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away and sparkling clean. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and well-maintained, you\u2019ve found it. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and ready for its next adventure with you!",
