    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my total pride and joy, and I\u2019ve babied it from day one\u2014always kept in the garage and kept spotless. It literally looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! The paint is flawless and the interior still has that fresh feeling. I'm only letting it go because I need something a bit bigger for the family, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
