    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the S65 4.0L V8 with its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and a reinforced subframe. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, supported by an Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system that performs to original tolerances. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock that remains tight and responsive. The exterior finish is devoid of rock chips or clear coat degradation, and the interior bolsters show zero compression or leather fatigue. A rare, investment-grade example for the technical purist.",
